{"tid":1877174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【天滅中共】湖北增242死 多逾1.4萬病例   十堰張灣區實施「戰時管制」","createTime":"2020-02-13T00:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:27:08.000Z","uid":186,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"a495ead8d671c6619f953bef19fbea75a82b10ce","tid":1877174,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"湖北增242死 多逾1.4萬病例   十堰張灣區實施<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「戰時管制」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國內地方面，在疫情最嚴重的中國湖北省，根據湖北衞健委今早公佈，全省新增確診病例14,840宗，新增病亡242宗，創下近日單日最高升幅。現時，湖北確診病例總數48,206宗，死亡宗數累計310宗。而全國的確診病例已暴升至近6萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n湖北十堰市張灣區疫情防控指揮部凌晨發佈通告，宣佈<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">張灣區全域從凌晨起實施戰時管制</span></strong></span>，管制措施原則上以14天為一周期，視全市及張灣區疫情防控效果予以提前解除或持續實施。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根據規定，區內所有樓宇一律實施全封閉管理，全部居民不得出入樓宇，基本生活必需品由鄉鎮、街道及村委會負責定時運送，急需藥物實行代購服務，物管人員廿四小時值班把守。</span></span>"},{"pid":"43731829fb411cc9109a6372a43e0d2d9bf46cf5","tid":1877174,"uid":186,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"戰時管制 = 戰爭狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天滅中共"},{"pid":"787a9ba19d4bd6ee1100f93bafd67adfab30536e","tid":1877174,"uid":186,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"香港人準備好戰爭狀況"},{"pid":"0bd649aceca11d34c01d33f96b0d752954f6975f","tid":1877174,"uid":29188,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E09gCDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE09gCDE.gif&h=99eeec2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a30a2f2d1f26b9374f8f1508a0604b3756ad082","tid":1877174,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,